The '''Benevolent Guides''', [[V-Tan]] and [[O-Vieve]], were responsible for creating the [[General Good|isolationist structure]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kegan/Legends|Kegan]]. However, their system was eventually rejected by the people. The Benevolent Guides lived within the [[Central Dwelling]] in the city of Kegan. Within the city's central coliseum inside the [[Gathering Circle]], the Guides moderated voting, allowing votes like in a democracy, but choosing which topics to vote on.<ref name="TFFT">''[[Jedi Apprentice: The Fight for Truth]]''</ref>

